  "A PVA model for an endangered salamander shows a 95% probability of extinction within 50 years at current population levels. However, if 100 hectares of wetland habitat is restored, the model predicts a 75% chance of survival. A developer offers to create a 100-hectare artificial pond instead. Why might the ecologist reject this alternative?": "",
